data.description: This one year old single story Mediterranean style home in the desirable community of Heritage Lake is a must see!!!! Whether you are a first time buyer, looking to raise a family in a great community or looking for an amazing place to retire, this home is for your...With 1920 sq ft. 3 Bed and 2 baths, it features high ceilings and an open floor plan that includes a large great room and an upgraded kitchen with granite counter tops, island kitchen and stainless steel appliances. The master suite features a walk in closet, his and hers sinks and a tub and stand alone shower. There is a separate laundry room and the house is prewired for surround sound and outside speakers. There is a tandem 3 car garage and the backyard is landscaped, including a concrete deck and sprinkler and drip system. The house sits on the corner in front of one of the parks and has to 2 side gates. Not to mention all the amenities that Heritage Lake has to offer, which include a huge lake, fishing, parks, a community club house with an Olympic size pool and spa, a water park, walking/biking trails, playgrounds, BBQ and picninc areas, sports parks, an elementary school and a middle school opening soon. And so much more.........
